Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.41,0:00:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}半死人：我  扼杀了自己的心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.13,0:00:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fs20}半死人：所以  我的名字是半死人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.71,0:00:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fs20}半死人：只有心  因为只有我的一半死了\N心要是继续活着  我会受不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.95,0:00:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈  这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.71,0:00:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.01,0:00:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『今天上课时也被人拿圆规针尖扎了背后』
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.49,0:00:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.74,0:00:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs20}要是发出声音会被老师发现的  只好拚命忍耐\N可是  无论怎么样做最后都叫出了声  今天被老师冷眼相看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.56,0:00:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fs21}某人：不能出声吗？  要是被欺负了  告诉老师如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.84,0:00:40.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是大人吗 真蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.48,0:00:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}某人：什么都不说最糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.11,0:00:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}某人：只会被欺负得更厉害而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.14,0:00:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}某人：在背后藏块铁板什么的（笑）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.64,0:00:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}某人：楼上太差劲了  要是你被欺负了  还说得出什么（笑）吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.23,0:00:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不用变得认真起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.28,0:00:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}某人：怎么会有这种人www
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.28,0:00:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}半死人：再不扼杀自己的心的话  我真的会受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.08,0:01:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}半死人：所以  我一直在扼杀自己的心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.45,0:01:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}半死人：让下一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.05,0:01:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}能成为新的（被欺负的）目标
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.86,0:02:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  安静下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今天起  这个书包就变为班上的垃圾桶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.22,0:02:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家满怀对菊川同学的谢意尽情使用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.71,0:03:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.29,0:03:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实  我们班上也有人被欺负
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.96,0:03:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  还算和平
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.90,0:03:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这比起被圆规针尖扎背  要强多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.53,0:03:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.64,0:03:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来今天是封挺好的死后文
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.01,0:03:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓好坏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.93,0:03:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死后文只是很诚实而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.94,0:03:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不诚实的只是人类而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.03,0:03:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其它的生物都很坦率的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.51,0:03:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那卡娜卡你为什么想成为人类呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.60,0:03:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为变成人以后  不就可以说谎了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.74,0:04:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.15,0:04:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱肉强食
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.64,0:04:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是现实的原则
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.35,0:04:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美川文歌  三年前开始住院
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后一直昏睡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.45,0:04:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  你见到的那名少女不是美川文歌 是其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.24,0:04:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不可能出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.98,0:04:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人？可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么美川会变成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.44,0:04:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.21,0:04:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察的保密义务？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.44,0:04:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为自己的工作感到自豪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  就告诉我一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.00,0:05:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美川…真的枪杀了…自己的父亲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.73,0:05:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.28,0:05:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弹痕也被确认了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.11,0:05:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  这些问题  由学号10 20 30的同学上来做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.29,0:05:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.17,0:05:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.42,0:05:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10号请假了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.44,0:05:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菊川  是你喔  10号
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.64,0:05:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  菊川
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.44,0:05:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我不会做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.82,0:05:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…那个啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.98,0:05:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会写多少写多少  写写看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.36,0:06:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.78,0:06:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}半死人：大家  晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.52,0:06:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}半死人：今天上课时被不准穿长裤和内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.65,0:06:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}某人：好丢人的表演出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.79,0:06:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}某人：升级了啊>欺负
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}某人：提问！半死人是女生吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.33,0:06:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}某人：请告诉我你是女生！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.76,0:06:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}某人：转校啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.38,0:06:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}半死人：快下课时被老师叫去黑板上做题  好丢人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.34,0:06:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}半死人：所以拚命地扼杀了自己的心  可怎么也死不了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.13,0:06:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  这不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.63,0:06:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.49,0:06:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}可燃垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.41,0:06:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半死人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.97,0:06:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我  森下同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛苦  已经是极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.05,0:07:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.62,0:07:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.66,0:07:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.26,0:07:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了  请救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.11,0:07:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要老依靠别人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.92,0:07:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是这样才被欺负的不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.52,0:07:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  错不在被欺负的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.83,0:07:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错的是欺负别人的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成绩很好  也打篮球
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都有洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.04,0:07:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初中时也被欺负过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.90,0:07:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.59,0:07:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  我很普通
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.99,0:07:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.14,0:07:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.98,0:07:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙激动过头了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 菊川也有朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦  说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.17,0:07:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用隐瞒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是好事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.30,0:08:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友情深厚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你们来交换下角色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『角色』的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.89,0:08:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又装傻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.29,0:08:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教室里需要一个这样的角色哟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.84,0:08:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个承担无聊的学生生活中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,压力的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.06,0:08:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是必不可少的恶意行为
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.55,0:08:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么可能是那家伙的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.02,0:08:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.17,0:08:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你来证明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.80,0:08:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.26,0:08:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是森下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.12,0:08:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森下？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天时你说要我救你对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.61,0:08:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.06,0:08:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？  真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.16,0:09:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  所以你现在来学校的屋顶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.33,0:09:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屋顶？ 现在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.76,0:09:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讨厌被欺负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.67,0:09:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森下  你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.14,0:09:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是菊川
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.07,0:09:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎欢迎  菊川
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天打算来做个游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.94,0:09:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『游戏』的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.70,0:09:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前看的漫画里有些有趣的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森下  你来解释下规则吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.00,0:09:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.51,0:09:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,规则很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.73,0:09:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里不是有条钢筋吗  走过去就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.14,0:09:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:09:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手碰到钢筋就算失败
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.15,0:10:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要从头再走一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.51,0:10:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人  这里可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.58,0:10:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬钢筋可是很累人的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.47,0:10:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好感谢我们哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.53,0:10:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  这样会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.70,0:10:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我去商店里偷东西的也好  什么我都做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.01,0:10:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.34,0:10:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.82,0:10:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就走过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.45,0:10:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么你都肯做不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.17,0:10:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配合下气氛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.13,0:10:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.91,0:10:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里禁止入内
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.88,0:10:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们有老师的许可吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.37,0:10:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我们是天文同好会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.77,0:10:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想来观测彗星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.40,0:10:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此  也不能擅自…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.32,0:10:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.77,0:10:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.94,0:10:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.03,0:10:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的隐形眼镜掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.97,0:10:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了  菊川
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.02,0:10:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  让人操心了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.57,0:11:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好险
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.24,0:11:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种游戏也太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.20,0:11:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}半死人：刚才有朋友的电话  看到我的留言说要救我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.55,0:11:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}某人：喔喔！救世主登场了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.52,0:11:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}某人：只是写着玩玩的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.91,0:11:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}半死人：我这就去  后续等我回来再写
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.37,0:11:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}某人：加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.00,0:11:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}某人：我等你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.97,0:11:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}某人：不想预测下发展吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.55,0:11:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}某人：我投期待落空一票
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}某人：不要赌——www
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.67,0:11:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他没有留言啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.69,0:11:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  今天救了你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.70,0:12:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后就靠自己努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.44,0:12:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半死人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.12,0:12:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  请肃静
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.35,0:12:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚  菊川公一去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.34,0:12:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从前几天的锁宅闭门不出事件以来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.94,0:12:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我校声誉不断受损
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是这种特殊时候  大家要注意自已的言行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.20,0:12:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调查将先在校园内进行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.29,0:12:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要对媒体说些多余的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.28,0:12:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位作为本校的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.12,0:12:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要做出有损学校荣誉的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.07,0:12:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs29}笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.74,0:13:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般会去死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.29,0:13:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知世事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.80,0:13:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那绝对不可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.19,0:13:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  他就是因此才被欺负的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.57,0:13:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.30,0:14:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于平静下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.30,0:14:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都过了一周了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.34,0:14:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各种新闻都有了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.56,0:14:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是被欺负了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.47,0:14:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自杀的一年级生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:27.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼稚的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…真想不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.56,0:14:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久前还一直认为
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.39,0:14:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死不过是老人身上或者发生战争的外国才有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.67,0:14:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到身边就有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.43,0:14:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs25}编写
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.43,0:14:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs25}半死人2
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.28,0:14:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  在被欺负
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.27,0:14:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于之前一直被欺负的人消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:14:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我成了新的牺牲品
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.61,0:15:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}不要来  去死  蛆虫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.40,0:15:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无视
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.28,0:15:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涂鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.30,0:15:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物品被藏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.94,0:15:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惯用的欺负手段
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.73,0:15:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}落榜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.61,0:15:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可一旦感受到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.30,0:15:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比想像中的要痛苦得多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.39,0:15:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁分很重要哟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.85,0:15:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得全世界都在与自己为敌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.83,0:15:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被扎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.85,0:15:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被打
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.57,0:15:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原以为这些比较严重
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.07,0:15:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实身心方面更痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.76,0:15:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次体会到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.07,0:15:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除我之外  还有被欺负过的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.20,0:15:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}编写
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.22,0:15:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}某人：有  被欺负过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.18,0:15:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.46,0:16:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}某人：笨蛋  怎么可能  不要把我归为同类  渣滓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.09,0:16:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}某人：这家伙  好早
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.24,0:16:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}某人：高兴吧  有同伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.85,0:16:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀死…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扼杀自己的心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.51,0:16:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久会出现下一个牺牲品了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.44,0:16:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前  我是个半死人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.09,0:16:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有全部死去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.85,0:16:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一半是死人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.94,0:16:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 无聊的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.08,0:16:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.72,0:16:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近森下你的回应方式太差
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做点游戏  让你开心一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.76,0:16:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.53,0:17:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天蒙着眼睛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『蒙着眼睛』？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.95,0:17:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能  肯定会掉下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游戏而已  赢了不就得了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.41,0:17:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊这是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.12,0:17:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是不死就不能换牺牲品了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.69,0:17:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死心吧  反正你逃不了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.69,0:17:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.37,0:17:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的学生？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.12,0:17:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这身打扮什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.88,0:17:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别随便碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.34,0:17:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这  这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.26,0:17:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs29}做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.88,0:17:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶~讨厌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.25,0:17:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 疼~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.83,0:17:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…等下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:17:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说了别把我当武器使吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.33,0:18:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得  得救了  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.26,0:18:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死后文
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.72,0:18:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死后的世界寄来的信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.99,0:18:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄信人是菊川公一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.21,0:18:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森下俊介
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.06,0:18:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你体会到了吗  我的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.98,0:18:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很难受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.09,0:18:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.49,0:18:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是多么地希望得到帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.41,0:18:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.23,0:18:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你和那些人狼狈为奸欺负我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.40,0:18:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活该
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.17,0:18:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.21,0:18:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.28,0:18:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有心死去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.84,0:18:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才刚刚开始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.80,0:18:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么给我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.15,0:18:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是救了你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.51,0:18:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.19,0:19:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森下认识的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.27,0:19:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就得让你来承担责任了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.84,0:19:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.56,0:19:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准逃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.47,0:19:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游戏还没结束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.34,0:19:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二回合
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.89,0:19:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开心点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.79,0:19:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会一直持续到早上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.00,0:19:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.30,0:19:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.18,0:19:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.16,0:19:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.42,0:19:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有心死去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.71,0:19:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走过去啊  不要忘记蒙住眼睛喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.43,0:19:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.99,0:19:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你抵抗个什么劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.48,0:19:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改为踢足球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.91,0:19:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜间比赛开始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.46,0:19:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来决赛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.15,0:19:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  玩夜间比赛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.83,0:20:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是菊川比较好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.81,0:20:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么…这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.54,0:20:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.81,0:20:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.44,0:20:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了那种人渣不得不进少管所哟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.53,0:20:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是为了保护自己而战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以牙还牙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.32,0:20:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是原始人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.52,0:20:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类被称为社会性的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.46,0:21:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  社会性的他死去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.16,0:21:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他作为动物却活下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.33,0:21:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}某人：半死人2后续！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.30,0:21:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fs20}> 11日深夜23点\N鸥冬高中屋顶发生了同校学生间的刺伤事件\N之前昏迷病危的F好像捡回一条命\N另外  刺伤少年F的少年A现在正在调查中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.60,0:21:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}某人：那个少年A是半死人2吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.76,0:21:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}某人：啊  那个被欺负的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.06,0:21:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}某人：所以才会杀人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}某人：看来我也得小心点了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.53,0:21:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}笨蛋  渣滓  恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.03,0:21:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}某人：你们也有过一两次经历吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.91,0:21:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}某人：发现被欺负的人！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.26,0:21:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}某人：像是打架双方同受惩罚？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.79,0:21:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}某人：不是那个意思啦（笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.17,0:21:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fnDFLiSong-Bd\i1\bord0\fs24}{\fad(300,500)}死後文\N\N第六話\N\N吶喊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.27,0:21:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.94,0:23:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停滞的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.52,0:23:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经如梦般的思绪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.40,0:23:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我定将
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.08,0:23:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切了结
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.96,0:23:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回  死后文
